comments: George (LAC) makes contact to Ayton's (PHX) arm during his shot attempt near the rim.
Crowder (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position during Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Ibaka (LAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Paul (PHX) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in George's (LAC) path.
Following the pass, George's (LAC) momentum carries him to but not through Booker (PHX) when the marginal contact occurs. Paul does not dislodge Booker.
Crowder (PHX) commits a take foul on Beverley (LAC).
George (LAC) makes contact to Bridges' (PHX) arm and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
